data.description: Looking for resort style living, second home or investment property in the desirable community of Hampton Estates. The current owner has maintained the property to a high standard and has made several upgrades including open concept kitchen, Nest thermostat programmable to smart phone, solar panels to reduce energy costs and a solar hot water heater with its own set of solar panels. LOWERED ELECTRIC BILLS. The open floor plan includes a separate dining room, kitchen and family room and downstairs master suite. The family room overlooks the screened in lanai with your very own pool. Community features tennis courts, sand volleyball and playground. Solar panels need to be transferred to the new owner as financing. There are NO CDD fees here! This espectacular home can also be use as a short term property.it will not last long! Call today for your private showing.
